Interface FormEditorConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NamedObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FormEditorConfigImpl

    public interface FormEditorConfig
extends NamedObject
    Configures a view of the form editor. Can be used as a "preferences" for the current user.
    Author:
    Jonathan Crosmer (jcrosmer@i2rd.com)
